Jessica Barden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessica_Barden 0 Jessica Barden ( born July 21, 1992) is an English actress best known for playing main character Alyssa in Channel 4 series The End of the F***ing World. Barden has also played the recurring character Justine in Penny Dreadful.
